des:
Amazon Alexa and the FairyNest products work together to help you control your LED light nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to change the LED's on/off, color, brightness. 

After connecting Alexa to your FairyHome products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "FairyHome" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one FairyHome account in our "FairyHome" app;
(3). You need to have some FairyHome devices in hand;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "FairyHome" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "FairyHome", and you'll be navigated to FairyHome login page;
(9). Input your FairyHome account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your LED light like these:
"Alexa, turn on living room light."
"Alexa, turn off living room light."
"Alexa, set living room light color to red."
"Alexa, set living room light to 20 percent."
"Alexa, dim living room light by 25 percent."
... ...
